Package jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.image

Class ImageBorder

java.lang.Object
jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.image.ImageBorder
public class ImageBorder
extends java.lang.Object
The class ImageBorder, which provides several image processing functions to handle X-Y and Z border. The X-Y and Z border should have to be safe to ensure that the filling function (filling holes) will work correctly. Date Created: Jun 18, 2015
Author:
Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
